snippet.title: Battlefield 10th Anniversary: Battlefield 2142 (2006)
snippet.description:
Celebrating 10 years of Battlefield, this is one of the classic trailers produced for Battlefield 2142.

Read our retrospective of Battlefield 2142 at the Battlefield Blog: http://bit.ly/UHRKDK

Stay tuned as we continue the Battlefield 10 year anniversary with more retrospectives, classic trailers, developer interviews, and reveals of old school concept art.
